#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cvendor-services.md:1
msgid "Vendor Services"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cvendor-services.md:3
msgid ""
"Alongside the government reference implementations of DMN decision models, "
"commercial vendors may offer certified implementations of the same decisions "
"with additional enterprise features, SLAs, and support. The Vendor Services "
"feature surfaces these implementations directly in the DMN list."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cvendor-services.md:12
msgid "Vendor badges"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cvendor-services.md:14
msgid ""
"A blue badge showing a count appears on any DMN card that has at least one "
"associated `ronl:VendorService` resource in TriplyDB. Clicking the badge "
"opens a modal with full details of all vendor implementations for that "
"decision model."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cvendor-services.md:18
msgid "Vendor detail modal"
msgstr ""

