msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cfeatures%5Cvendor-services.md:34
msgid ""
"Vendor implementations are published to TriplyDB via the CPSV Editor's "
